# Event Ledger conventions

- Canonical architecture & scope: [`PROJECT.md`](PROJECT.md), locked decisions: [`SPECS.md`](SPECS.md)
- Java 21 + Spring Boot 3.4 multi-module (`event-gateway`, `account-service`)
- Sync REST only between services; no Kafka broker in v1
- Prefer existing patterns: `ErrorResponse`, `ResponseStatusException`, Resilience4j annotations
- Tests: JUnit 5 + MockMvc (+ WireMock/Pact in gateway)
- Observability: JSON logs → Loki, OTLP → Jaeger, Micrometer → Prometheus/Grafana

When diagnosing health, run the **diagnose-event-ledger** skill or `/diagnose` command.
